        style="
          color: #ddd;
          background-color: #282e34;
          text-align: center;
          padding: 50px 80px;
          text-align: justify;
        "
      >
        <h1>Here is how we work</h1>
        <br />
        <p>
          Click on the desired form. Fill the form. Get the pdf. Authenticate it
