        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bgimg-3">
      <div class="caption">
        <span
          class="border"
          style="background-color: #666699; font-size: 25px; color: white"
          >EFFICIENCY</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="position: relative">
      <div
        style="
          color: #ddd;
          background-color: #282e34;
          text-align: center;
          padding: 50px 80px;
          text-align: justify;
        "
